# This directory is Karaf's hot-deploy folder, mounted at /opt/karaf/deploy
# inside the fzl-karaf-camel-integration container.
# Karaf writes runtime state files here (.deployed tracking files, etc.).
# Nothing in this directory should be committed to git.
#
# Blueprint XML bundles live in:
#   src-projects/karaf_bundles/blueprint-xmls-bundles/
# They are copied here by entrypoint.sh before Karaf starts.
*
!.gitignore
